      • gridElementSettings

        @Contract(pure=true)
public static java.awt.GridBagConstraints gridElementSettings(int row,
                                                                                   int column,
                                                                                   int width,
                                                                                   int height)
        Returns a GridBagConstraints object with the following properties:
        • row and column parameters translate directly into GridBagConstraints.gridy and GridBagConstraints.gridx fields of the returned object respectively
        • the width and height parameter translates to GridBagConstraints.gridwidth and fields GridBagConstraints.gridheight fields of the returned object respectively, which means it will take up space of that much grid columns and rows
        Parameters:
        row - vertical position in the grid
        column - horizontal position in the grid
        width - determines the component width (in terms of grid columns)
        height - determines the component height (in terms of grid rows)
        Returns:
        a GridBagConstraints instance
